<br>
In our early days, we had a very good relationship with GoL and generally, if we had a shot at something big, we'd share the adventure with GoL.  Most won't even remember wtf I'm talking about, but GoL helped us on our first AD kill.  Things were great, we were growing fast and we respected each other.  Then somewhere along the way we stopped inviting them along, maybe we wanted to try things solo, who knows why but we went our seperate ways.<br>
<br>
Since those days, we've had a few run ins with GoL, nothing serious.  It's to be expected for 2 guilds of near strength and similar goals to bump heads now and then.  Most of our meetings ended up in a fairly professional manner.  Klandicar?  I'm not going to side topic here, but Kland is a farmable joke.  If you wait long enough, someone, somewhere is going to get tired of waiting and engage for you.<br>
<br>
Most recently FotC lost a husband and wife duo to GoL that left on rather bad terms.  Oh, they took a croanie with them, but he's besides the point.  Since that time, our relationship with GoL has turned ugly and I can't help to think that it's spurred from scorned ex-members of FotC.<br>
<br>
The bottom line is this, not one time since FotC was formed, have we ever treated any guild in this fashion, nor has any other guild stooped to these new lows against us.  Yes, we've had our run ins with other guilds, but they've never enaged a mob that we were killing until it was regened.  And we have never done it to anyone else either.  FotC has had it's share of bad press, thanks to so many colorful personalities that we picked up in such a short time, which for the most part are now gone from our roster thank goodness.<br>
<br>
As for the loot, and the possibility of splitting it or having it handed to us, don't flatter yourselves.  Fuck the loot.  We'll get our own next time we kill AoW.  Enjoy the toys we farmed for you.  What I would like to see is some GM disciplinary action, but I'm not dilusional either. <p><!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=467339" target="top">Rokjaw Preechurfysts - Officer of Fate of the Chosen</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--> <!--EZCODE BR START--><br /><!--EZCODE BR END--> <!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=571595" target="top">Godzirra &quot;Dream Monk&quot;</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--> </p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub40.ezboard.com/bthesaryrntavern.showUserPublicProfile?gid=jamhet69>jamhet69</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle><span style='color:pink;'>Tavern Floor Sweeper</span></span><br>  Posts: 12<br> <font color=#6FB8DD>(7/11/03 12:37 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub40.ezboard.com/fthesaryrntavernthefurnace.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=3374.topic&index=135>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: re</span><hr size=1> wow one thing surprises me, spyrit has NOT posted here yet, holy shit, that's all we need to round up the entire dickshit clan on saryrn server. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#242422><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub40.ezboard.com/bthesaryrntavern.showUserPublicProfile?gid=limeessence@thesaryrntavern>LimeEssence</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle><span style='color:pink;'>Tavern Floor Sweeper</span></span><br>  Posts: 15<br> <font color=#6FB8DD>(7/11/03 12:42 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub40.ezboard.com/fthesaryrntavernthefurnace.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=3374.topic&index=136>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m>